================================================================================

SentinelQA's first-party source code is Apache-2.0. The repository
vendors a small number of upstream JSON Schemas / XSDs at
`packages/shared-schema/external/` so the build does not depend on
fetching them at runtime. Each upstream remains under its own
license; SentinelQA does not relicense them.

